t what your friends do.<br><br>You are the Lightbringer, Talania. I see that this has dimmed you a bit, chin up! In the short time that I've known you, I know that you will bounce back. This is really very little compared to other things in life, is it not?<br><br>/smiles Talania<br>/hugs Talania<br>/leans shoulder a little closer<br><br>Axardis@hotmail.com, if you need me.<br><br>Smitten D'Zyer<br>Elf of many faces and many alts. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub47.ezboard.com/uaalaandro.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aalaandro</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Fluffy </span><br>  Posts: 1137<br> <font color=#ffff00>(2/11/02 9:39:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub47.ezboard.com/faquiloarcisfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=441.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Chin up, girl!</span><hr size=1> Tala, you know that Malasa and I will always have room for you in our group. We will always take time to talk to you. Please, I know how much this crap in AdiA is making you feel horrible, don't let it get to you. Remember that throughout it all, you can log on, and say hello to your husband, and your friends.<br><br>No matter what guild either of us end up in, you're going to stay on my friend's list forever. /hugs <p><img src="http://jennymarie.freewebspace.com/aal-new-sig.gif"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub47.ezboard.com/uainthara.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ainthara</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>AdA Member</span><br>  Posts: 175<br> <font color=#ffff00>(2/11/02 9:43:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub47.ezboard.com/faquiloarcisfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=441.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://eq.weezul.net/ainthara/flamingdevildee.gif width=110 he